data.name: description1.Text
data.value: A bouquet of red roses accompanied by white statice. A bouquet wrapped to perfection and suitable for any occasions as red roses simply symbolizes your passion, true love and desire while leaving the white statice to portray your utmost sincerity. This is the go-to gift that expresses your love and intentions without having to say a word.

data.name: description3.Text
data.value: A classic arrangement of ravishing red roses, paired together with pretty-in-pink petals and sprays of lush foliage. Treat them to the Petal Perfect experience on their special day, to put the widest smile on their face, or simply just because - with the perfect mini bouquet for those cherished moments.

data.name: description10.Text
data.value: When words fail, express your love with flowers. Let your significant other know the depths of your devotion with this enchanting mini bouquet, featuring stunning blooms such as pink roses and a pink lily. Have it delivered to their doorstep today as a surprise that will make them love you even more!

data.name: description9.Text
data.value: Surprise that special someone, with the refined beauty of our Ivory Elegance flower bouquet, featuring a graceful arrangement of pristine white carnations with bursts of vibrant red berries, thoughtfully arranged amid sprays of lush foliage. Encapsulating a sense of wonderful sophistication, this bouquetserves as a perfect expression of your admiration, best wishes and love.

data.name: description8.Text
data.value: Bring a sun-filled smile to their face and set their heart aflutter with our incredibly adorable Sunlight Posy flower bouquet. Topped with radiant yellow gerberas and accompanied by a mix of lush foliage, this lively mini bouquet is guaranteed to infuse their day with rays of happiness and add an extra bounce in their step.

data.name: description7.Text
data.value: Brighten their day with a touch of Mauve Magic, with a bouquet of blossoms radiating fondness and affection. Featuring a bunch of soft purple blooms, accented with sprays of lush foliage, this charming mini bouquet is a sweet and simple way to convey your love and best wishes.

data.name: description5.Text
data.value:
Indulge in a whole lot of Delicious Love - with the perfect present for just about anyone in your life! A bouquet filled with hazelnut-infused, choco-liscious Ferrero Rochers, wrapped together delicately is exactly what everyone needs, to make their day super sweet!
- with 20 pcs Ferrero Rocher

data.name: description2.Text
data.value: Made worthy for a princess - with soft pink gerberas, roses, and carnations, and frills of white aster. Our Anneliese flower bouquet the sweetest gesture of tender, loving care to truly light up her day.
